MAJOR UPDATE Status and Skill "Seeing" based on original images is now a reality. Before numbered hash codes were used to determine skills and statuses, this created an issue when going from one machine to another as the codes did not always match the same skills and statuses on a new machine. Status and Skill "Seeing" allows for the machine to make the hashcodes itself based on an image library. This means you will no longer have to specify what skills you have in your hotkeys, it will read them (with a few exceptions). For my next trick, Items will have their own image library.
